metadata.name: (icon) Tarot - The Fool
metadata.description:
#0 - The Fool

Mark pontificates at the shores of Hinnom before embarking on his most dangerous quest yet.


About the Project:

(icon) Tarot is a deck showcasing your favorite characters and creatures from the Gospel of Mark. 

Collectors of 7 out of the 70+ cards will get a free collectors edition of the deck when it's compiled.

People who collect ALL 70+ cards in the deck will be gifted a custom 1/1 art piece and be inducted into the (icon)DAO.
